; L13: Multi-Box Cooperation (Extended Tutorial)
; Grid: 9-col x 6-row (x: 0-8, y: 0-5)
; Player at (1,1), Box1 at (2,2) top=NORMAL, Box2 at (6,2) top=IMPACT
; Button at (4,3) requires NORMAL, Door at (5,3)
; Solution: push Box1 onto button, push Box2 through door, both complete
; This teaches: different boxes can serve different purposes simultaneously

[node name="Level13" type="Node3D"]
script = ExtResource("1")
start_hint_text = "两个箱子可以同时工作。各有各的用处。"
completed_hint_text = "多箱协作完成。按 R 可以重开。"

